      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW ZENITH (3) is having his first look at this circuit. Comes here an impressive winner latest at Warragul in a Grade 4/5 in one of the quickest times of the program (26.01). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Looks the testing material. DR. LEVIATE (6) has a terrific record this track and trip with four wins and four placings from eight starts. Was out of the placings last time (30.13) at Sandown in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 8 lengths. Can feature in the finish. MY NAME'S EDEN (7) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (22.82) from Box 5 at Warragul. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and two minor placings from eight starts. Can measure up. JUMBUK BAYEH (1) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot at big odds most recently.",
